grid.text: 4. Cloud fan over Flipped L. sleeve
4. Resetting L. sleeve, take seven steps to 3.
5. Waki slides to face the shite
8. Fan to the L. hand, R. Circlet

captions.translation: [SHITE] "As my final home I have shown you
captions.transcription: [SHITE] Tsui no yadori wa shirase mo-ōshitsu.
captions.japaneseScript: ［シテ］終の宿りは知らせ申しつ。

captions.translation: [SHITE] I beg you", she said, and
[JIUTAI] as she spoke the crowing of the cocks,
[SHITE] The tolling of the bells too,
[JIUTAI] As nothing will be hidden in the morning light,
captions.japaneseScript: ［地謡］あさまにもなりぬべし。

captions.translation: "Before dawn breaks, to the dwelling of the "evening face",
captions.transcription: Akenu saki ni to iugao no yadori.
captions.japaneseScript: 明けぬ先にと夕顔の宿り。

captions.translation: "before dawn breaks, to the dwelling of the "evening face",
captions.transcription: Akenu saki ni to iugao no yadori no.
captions.japaneseScript: 明けぬ先にと夕顔の宿りの。

captions.translation: she says, and again goes within the lattice shutter,
captions.transcription: Mata hashitomi no uchi ni irite,

captions.translation: just so, becoming one with the dream.
captions.transcription: sono mama yume to zo nari ni keru.
captions.japaneseScript: 其まま夢とぞなりにける。
